<ul>
<li><span class="citation book">Habib, Adam (2013). <i>South Africa's suspended revolution - Hopes and prospects</i>. Wits University Press. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-86814-608-6" title="Special:BookSources/978-1-86814-608-6">978-1-86814-608-6</a>.</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAdam+Habib&amp;rft.aufirst=Adam&amp;rft.au=Habib%2C+Adam&amp;rft.aulast=Habib&amp;rft.btitle=South+Africa%27s+suspended+revolution+-+Hopes+and+prospects&amp;rft.date=2013&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-86814-608-6&amp;rft.pub=Wits+University+Press&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
